text: David Helísek (born 4 September 1982) is a Czech football midfielder who currently plays for Hodonín. ==Career== In July 2019, after seven seasons with Znojmo, Helísek joined Hodonín.Návrat zpět, vyhlašuje cíl Hodonín.
